<h1>Blacklisted for abuse</h1>

<p>
  This request has been blacklisted for sending too much traffic to <code>{{config.devDomain}}</code>. Please contact the owner of the site that sent you here and ask them to use <code>{{config.cdnDomain}}</code> instead, which has no traffic limit.
</p>

<p>
